OL,3,CWhere will your tip go? New law stops
OL,4,Cbusinesses pocketing staff tips
OL,6,FA new law has come into force meaning
OL,7,Fstaff must be given 100% of all tips
OL,8,For service charges.
OL,10,FFrom Tuesday businesses such as pubs,
OL,11,Frestaurants, cafes and taxi firms are
OL,12,Fno longer allowed to keep any tips
OL,13,Fpaid by their customers and must share
OL,14,Fthem among their workers.
OL,16,FTips must now be passed to employees
OL,17,Fby the end of the following month from
OL,18,Fwhen they were received.
