OL,3,CWhere will your tip go? New law stops
OL,4,Cbusinesses pocketing staff tips
OL,6,FAgency workers will also be entitled
OL,7,Fto the tips as part of the rules.
OL,9,FThe change comes eight years after a
OL,10,Fgovernment report first suggested the
OL,11,Fpolicy could be introduced following a
OL,12,Freview.
OL,14,FThis came after a number of companies,
OL,15,Fparticularly casual dining
OL,16,Frestaurants, came under criticism over
OL,17,Ftheir tips policies.
