OL,3,CWhere will your tip go? New law stops
OL,4,Cbusinesses pocketing staff tips
OL,6,FKate Nicholls, chief executive of
OL,7,Findustry body UKHospitality, said:
OL,8,F"The people working in hospitality are
OL,9,Fthe lifeblood of our sector and these
OL,10,Fchanges rightly ensure tips hard-
OL,11,Fearned through excellent service will
OL,12,Fend up entirely in their pockets.
OL,14,F"We completely support the changes
OL,15,Fcoming into effect today, which will
OL,16,Fformalise what is already commonplace
OL,17,Fin the sector as businesses have been
OL,18,Fpreparing for this legislation for a
OL,19,Fnumber of years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
